        {
            "title": "萬科再獲喘息 即將到期債券的持有人同意延長寬限期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"萬科再獲喘息 即將到期債券的持有人同意延長寬限期\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"545\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.rj.Hmt5CL6LDQUctNZ8Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/4c990560-cb7e-11f0-a6ff-97f99d22db0c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">萬科再獲喘息 即將到期債券的持有人同意延長寬限期</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
