        {
            "title": "澤連斯基將與特朗普會面 俄方表態令和平協議前景受到質疑",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"澤連斯基將與特朗普會面 俄方表態令和平協議前景受到質疑\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wQn.Pc9mrgv6TpiNgTGKQg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/a45d9530-e2e5-11f0-a7b7-4a228e8c0e9c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">澤連斯基將與特朗普會面 俄方表態令和平協議前景受到質疑</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
