        {
            "title": "澤連斯基與川普會晤前夕 基輔遭到俄羅斯大規模空襲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在烏克蘭總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:澤連斯基;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/澤連斯基\">澤連斯基</a>與美國總統川普會商俄烏休戰計畫的前夕，俄羅斯軍隊對烏克蘭首都發動了大規模空襲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">持續了九個多小時的無人機和飛彈襲擊造成基輔一人死亡、至少19人受傷，供電和供水中斷，並引發多處火災。這座擁有300多萬居民、氣溫徘徊在冰點附近的城市中，約有三分之一的地區斷了暖氣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">基輔市長Vitali Klitschko在一系列Telegram帖子中表示，多棟多層住宅樓著火，汽車和其他財物也被燒毀。他說有11人入院。當局在首都實施了緊急斷電，取代原定的輪流停電計畫，同時供水也中斷。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e226eb29-3ded-3d94-ac15-2d7476aa89a0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">烏克蘭能源部表示，大基輔地區和烏克蘭北部的切爾尼戈夫地區也發生了停電。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基與川普將於周日在佛羅里達州棕櫚灘會面，以爭取達成協議結束俄羅斯長達近四年的入侵。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澤連斯基周五告訴Axios，如果俄羅斯同意至少停火60天，他準備將最終的框架協議提交全民公投。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：澤連斯基將與川普會面 俄方表態令和平協議前景受到質疑</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Kyiv Hit by Russian Barrage a Day Before Zelenskiy-Trump Meeting</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E8%88%87%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95-%E5%9F%BA%E8%BC%94%E9%81%AD%E5%88%B0%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E7%A9%BA%E8%A5%B2-084144059.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-27 19:25:51",
